parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: VSC TRAC and ABS System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the VSC TRAC and ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The VSC TRAC
ABS
and brake lights come on
the vehicle slows down or loses power
grinding noise when braking
and loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents or loss of control, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
loss of control
and difficulty stopping.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failure can cause accidents or loss of control, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
grinding noise when braking
and loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to slow down or stop
loud grinding or buzzing noise
vibration in the pedal
and illumination of warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The ABS warning light illuminates
the vehicle's brakes seize or vibrate
the vehicle slides or pulls to one side
and loud grinding or buzzing noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the VSC system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The VSC warning light illuminates
the vehicle's brakes seize or vibrate
the vehicle slides or pulls to one side
and loud grinding or buzzing noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the airbag recall can lead to a higher risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the faulty airbag inflators may not deploy properly or may deploy with excessive force.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the recall repair process rather than a malfunction of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: VSC Traction Control Light and Acceleration Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning VSC traction control system can cause the vehicle to accelerate poorly, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The VSC traction control light comes on
the check engine light comes on
the vehicle accelerates poorly
and the vehicle can slow down dramatically at high speeds.
